          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " to a letter to the Obama Department of Health and Human Services calling on officials to broadly use ‚Äúmarch-in rights‚Äù to lower the cost of prescription drugs ‚Äî including ‚Äúspecialty drugs, like those to treat cancer, which are frequently developed with taxpayer funds.‚Äù",
