        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "In this case, the patent on Xtandi is held by pharma giant Astellas, which in turn shares the U.S. market with Pfizer. Xtandi has proven to be effective in treating prostate cancer, and is ",
            "type": "text",
